Citation.sAbstract: Vapor liquid equilibrium (VLE), liquid liquid equilibrium (LLE), and vapor liquid liquid equilibrium (VLLE) data were measured for the ternary mixture of 1-octyl-3-methylimidazolium hexafluorophosphate ([OMIM][PF6]), butan-1-ol, and butyl acetate. Results showed that the selectivity of butan-1-ol and butyl acetate can be enhanced by ionic liquid [OMIM][PF6]. The experimental VLE and LLE data were correlated using NRTL model, and the calculated values agreed well with the experimental values.
Citation.sTitle: Phase Equilibrium (VLE, LLE, and VLLE) Data of the Ternary System: Ionic Liquid [OMIM][PF6] + Butan-1-ol + Butyl Acetate
